   <head>Epigrammi - XXI. De Barth. Platina.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1">Ingenia, et mores, vitasque, obitusque notasse</l>
     <l n="2">Pontificum, argutae lex fuit historiae.</l>
     <l n="3">Tu tamen hinc laurae tractas pulmenta culinae:</l>
     <l n="4">Hoc, Platina, est, ipsos pascere pontifices.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
